{"type": "article", "id": 16417, "title": "BeoPlay H7", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-22T07:01:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 60, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000342bL0iXUHDuZS1My52.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦音响品牌 Bang &amp; Olufsen 日前推出新款无线耳机 BeoPlay H7，外形与 H6 和 H8 都有些类似，使用去氧化的铝合金和皮质耳罩，只是皮质耳罩更大。这款耳机可以提供连续20小时的电，另配一根插线，能直接插在设备上当做有线耳机使用。有两种颜色可选，浅棕色皮搭配银色或深黑色。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143713jOmWlx8b2SrKAhF6.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143713BrNSM8cOEtUPsxwp.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143714QwX84hBlICEFr7qP.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143715RWHS1vNwhO3MFEn8.jpg\" width=\"478\" height=\"670\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.40167364\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}